  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C).",
    "Season the tiger prawns with garam masala, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Place the pita bread slices on a baking sheet and toast in the oven for 5 minutes.",
    "In a large bowl, whisk together olive oil, lemon juice, and garlic.",
    "Add the mixed greens, cherry tomatoes, and red onion to the bowl and toss to combine.",
    "Add the toasted pita bread to the bowl and toss again.",
    "Add the raw tiger prawns to the bowl and toss gently to combine.",
    "Divide the fattoush salad among four plates.",
    "Top each plate with a salt-baked tiger prawn and serve immediately.",
    "Bake the tiger prawns in the oven for 8-10 minutes, or until pink and cooked through."
